subtitleNullable: A comprehensive dataset of residential property in the city of edmonton
descriptionNullable:
This dataset provides a comprehensive collection of residential property characteristics, sales data, and trends for the Edmonton housing market. It includes information on the sale prices, square footage, number of bedrooms and bathrooms, lot size, year built, and other attributes of the properties.

In addition to property characteristics, the dataset also includes information on the neighborhoods and geographic locations of the properties, allowing for a detailed analysis of the regional housing market. The dataset can be used to analyze trends and patterns in housing prices, inventory, and availability, as well as to develop predictive models for future home prices and sales.
